{"type":null,"faqId":34064,"title":" Can I use my phone as a mobile Wi-Fi hotspot and access the Internet from another device using my phone's data connection?","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:end;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{font-weight:bold;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>Yes. To activate this, turn on the Wi-Fi hotspot on your phone as follows:</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>Choose </span><span class=\"s1\">Settings</span><span> &gt; </span><span class=\"s1\">Wireless &amp; networks</span><span> &gt; </span><span class=\"s1\">More</span><span> &gt; </span><span class=\"s1\">Tethering &amp; portable hotspot</span><span> &gt; </span><span class=\"s1\">Portable Wi-Fi hotspot</span><span>.</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=109379\" style=\"width:1.9694444in;height:3.5041666in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=109380\" style=\"width:1.9680556in;height:3.5in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=109381\" style=\"width:1.9680556in;height:3.5in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>After a device connects to your phone over Wi-Fi, you can access the Internet from that device using your phone's mobile data connection.</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>To set the hotspot name and encryption mode, choose </span><span class=\"s1\">Settings</span><span> &gt; </span><span class=\"s1\">Wireless &amp; networks</span><span> &gt; </span><span class=\"s1\">More</span><span> &gt; </span><span class=\"s1\">Tethering &amp; portable hotspot</span><span> &gt; </span><span class=\"s1\">Portable Wi-Fi hotspot settings</span><span>.</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=109382\" style=\"width:1.9680556in;height:3.5in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  ></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":null,"faqType":null,"useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":244,"languageName":"mm","faqCode":"8764","faqTypeCode":null,"isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436779652000,"seriesProductName":"CHC-U01","visitedTimes":1,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"CHC-U01,G play mini","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}